entry.title: Endemic Covid-19 Has Arrived in Portugal. This Is What It Looks Like.
entry.content: The country has one of the world’s highest coronavirus vaccination rates. Its cautious return to normality is being closely watched by other countries as their inoculations inch higher.

entry.title: French Nationalist TV Host Éric Zemmour, Inspired by Trump, Surges in Polls
entry.content: Far-right pundit explores a presidential run in France, assembling a new electoral coalition that is siphoning off support from longtime standard-bearer Marine Le Pen and shaking up French politics.
